➜上海移动式核酸检测实验室正式交付
http://www.sohu.com/a/412029195_267106	51461
<p><img src="//p0.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200807/427e16d8f41a44f097710ca85a6a3c11.jpeg" /></p>
